@database PkbClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Pkb Class"


Pkb class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "VirtgroupClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Pkb class is used to create piano keyboard images in a
  virtual group.

  Pkb class is a subclass of Pkb.mcc, so you must have Pkb.mcc in
  MUI:Libvs/MUI to use it. Pkb.mcc is copyright of Calogero
  CALI'.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}PkbMode@{fg text}
  S ISGN
  G2N One of:
     o Normal
     o Special
     o Range

  @{fg shine}PkbAutoRelease@{fg text}
  B ISGN

  @{fg shine}PkbCurrent@{fg text}
  N ISGN

  @{fg shine}PkbQuiet@{fg text}
  B S

  @{fg shine}PkbOctvName@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}PkbOctvBase@{fg text}
  N I

  @{fg shine}PkbOctvRange@{fg text}
  N I

  @{fg shine}PkbOctvStart@{fg text}
  N IGN

  @{fg shine}PkbKeyRelease@{fg text}
  N SN

  @{fg shine}PkbKeyPress@{fg text}
  N S

  @{fg shine}PkbRangeHead@{fg text}
  S SGN G2N
  One of:
     o Off
     o Bop
     o Top

  @{fg shine}PkbRangeStart@{fg text}
  N SGN

  @{fg shine}PkbRangeEnd@{fg text}
  N SGN

  @{fg shine}PkbLow@{fg text}
  N G

  @{fg shine}PkbHigh@{fg text}
  N G

  @{fg shine}PkbInputEnable@{fg text}
  B ISGN

  @{fg shine}PkbExcludeLow@{fg text}
  B ISGN

  @{fg shine}PkbExcludeHigh@{fg text}
  B ISGN

  @{fg shine}PkbType@{fg text}
  S IGN G2N
  One of:
     o Normal
     o Small

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  @{fg shine}PkbJump@{fg text}
  <ncode/N>

  @{fg shine}PkbRange@{fg text}
  <start/N>,<end/N>

  @{fg shine}PkbRangeRefresh@{fg text}
  -

  @{fg shine}PkbRangeReset@{fg text}
  -

  @{fg shine}PkbRefresh@{fg text}
  -

  @{fg shine}PkbReset@{fg text}
  -

@EndNode

